Encfs is a virtual encrypted file system. It is built on top of [[FUSE]] and is really easy to use.

This is how I use it:
<pre class="sh_sh">
encfs `pwd`/encdocs `pwd`/mntdocs
EncFS Password:
</pre>

The first time I entered that command, I was prompted with a few questions first.

